          "scid": "thig1.16:1.0.3",
          "en": "16. Sumanā (Who left the world when old)"
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig1.16:1.0.4",
          "en": "“Happily rest, thou venerable dame! Rest thee, wrapt in the robe thyself hast made. Stilled are the passions that have raged within. Cool art thou now, knowing Nibbana’s peace.”"
        }
